itemLabel: Gordon Macdonald, 1st Baron Macdonald of Gwaenysgor

wikipedia_page.main: Gordon Macdonald, 1st Baron Macdonald of Gwaenysgor  (27 May 1888 – 20 January 1966) was a British Labour Party politician and Newfoundland's final British governor as well as the last chairman of the Commission of Government serving from 1946 until the colony joined Confederation in 1949 and became a province of Canada.
